data.description: Back on the market with no fault of Sellers.  Come see our charming, family friendly property for sale in Pinehurst, NC.  This large home offers a light and airy ambiance with an inviting open floor plan.  The bi-level living creates a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. The Primary Bedroom is conveniently  located on the main floor, complete with a generously sized closet and a luxurious bathroom designed for two. On the main floor you will find two additional bedrooms and a bathroom.With two bedrooms and a sizable recreation room downstairs, this home provides ample space for family members and guests.The fully fenced backyard ensures privacy and security, allowing you to enjoy outdoor activities such as relaxing around the fire pit or a game of basket ball.   The large deck overlooking the patio below is a perfect spot for unwinding, hosting gatherings, or enjoying meals outdoors.
